{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-archived-blog-template-js","path":"/2014/02/delicious-steps-in-asia-table/","result":{"data":{"archivedBlogPostJson":{"categories":[{"path":"/category/entertainment/","name":"生活娱乐活动"}],"tags":[{"name":"万达","path":"/tag/wanda/"},{"name":"亚洲土地","path":"/tag/asia-table/"},{"name":"大楚网","path":"/tag/dachu/"},{"name":"新年","path":"/tag/new-year/"},{"name":"春节","path":"/tag/spring-festival/"},{"name":"武汉","path":"/tag/wuhan/"},{"name":"祝福","path":"/tag/blessing/"},{"name":"舞蹈","path":"/tag/dance/"},{"name":"餐厅","path":"/tag/restaurant/"},{"name":"魏梦瑶","path":"/tag/mengyao/"}],"featured_media":{"source_url":"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/cover2.jpg"},"path":"/2014/02/delicious-steps-in-asia-table/","date":"2014-02-08T11:16:42.000Z","excerpt":"在YouTube上播放 2014-01-28，2014春节前夕，与梦瑶去汉街万达的亚洲土地餐厅，Cathy和她 … ","title":"亚洲土地的美味步伐(Delicious Steps in Asia Table)","content":"<p><object width=\"480\" height=\"400\" align=\"middle\" codebase=\"http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0\" classid=\"clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000\"><param name=\"src\" value=\"http://player.youku.com/player.php/sid/XNjY5Njc0NzQw/v.swf\"/><param name=\"allowfullscreen\" value=\"true\"/><param name=\"quality\" value=\"high\"/><param name=\"allowscriptaccess\" value=\"always\"/><embed width=\"480\" height=\"400\" align=\"middle\" src=\"http://player.youku.com/player.php/sid/XNjY5Njc0NzQw/v.swf\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" quality=\"high\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\"/></object></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B6xXoB1lLls\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">在YouTube上播放</a></p>\n<p>2014-01-28，2014春节前夕，与梦瑶去汉街万达的亚洲土地餐厅，Cathy和她朋友们热情洋溢的音乐和舞步让美味更添欢乐。在这里与美丽高贵又善解人意的梦瑶共进晚餐，以此作为2013年最后一个美好回忆，不禁让我期盼2014年新的精彩。<br />\nThanks Cathy, Romel, Christian, Yao Ming, and Jackie Chan. You&#8217;re so kind, using your music and dancing steps bring happiness to people.Happy Chinese New Year!<br />\n祝我们新年快乐！</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2014/02/delicious-steps-in-asia-table/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","3675143411","4019104361"]}